A trophy wife decides to send her unruly daughter to an upper class girl's academy where students are supposed to be subjected to a bit more severe discipline than in ordinary schools. "You'll learn some discipline, respect and cooperation. If you give it a chance and put away your attitude problem!"
name: Dark Cabin

description: A mother and her two daughters are detained for interrogation. Their beauty is spectacular and their captors decide to take their time with them...
name: SS Prison Hell

description: A beautiful lieutenant and a private are in a low risk mission far from their quarters...
name: War Slaves, Part 1

description: The maintenance people lusted after them for months. The girls were the hottest cockteasers on the campus...
name: Cheerleaders In Chains

description: Sweat pouring down her brow, Judith Denton ran through the the woods she had played in as a child. Her thoughts streaked back and forth between those carefree days and the last few days of her first year in College.
name: Cabin Fever

description: A hot young Hollywood starlet in the hands of a white slavery ring!
name: Star Fuckers 2

description: ...And one morning, as humanity had been warned for many many years, it happened. It all came to an end.
name: Circus Armageddon

description:
Outside,unnoticed by the neighbors, they have been there every morning for the last 3 weeks. Inside mom is preparing breakfast, elder sis is taking a shower and Heather, the younger of the two sisters, is still in bed. Dad’s car has just left the suburban house...

And it’s time to rush in!
name: Black Van 4 - Home Invasion

description: One of the darkest secrets of America ’s powerful elite is a beautiful forest resort in Northern California known as The Grove. Owned by a private club of the world’s most rich and powerful, every year it hosts a week long celebration of hedonism, idol worship, and unrestrained sexual perversion.
name: The Grove

description: Young women are taken from all over Europe and brought to the Inquisition Tribunal to be tried for practicing the dark arts. It shouldn't be a crime to be young and beautiful, but that's all it takes for the unfortunate women who catch the lust-crazed eye of the pitiless WITCH HUNTERS. These ruthless flesh merchants who patrol Europe are paid a handsome bounty for every attractive woman they capture.None are guilty, just too beautiful. But it makes no difference, none of the women taken into custody will ever be free again...
name: Witch Hunt

description:
A beautiful blonde girl finds herself at the mercy
of a ruthless masked man, deep in a dark warehouse. She soon learns there are TWO men, and one has her younger Sister!
name: Slave Sisters

description: Come with us now to a world that only lives in most men's dreams. A world of the ultra-rich and powerful, where anything can be bought if your money is unlimited. Including the most beautiful young women on earth, to do with whatever your most perverse dreams require to fulfill. In a secret location on an island resort for the rich, no girl is safe, no price too high, no sex act forbidden. The most wanted and desirable are brought to the compound, bought and sold, coerced and enslaved, to be used and abused at the whim of the super rich.
name: The Collection

description: Amanda peacefully sleeps in her bed. Suddenly, a huge hand on her mouth wakes her up with a start. A masked man in dark clothes is next to her bed!
name: The Dungeon Next Door

description: Locked away in the darkest vaults of the most sinister, sadistic mind to ever walk the web, only now could we finally reveal the continuation of his latest and greatest masterpiece...
name: The Black Van 5 - Home Invasion 2

description: Professor Woodley and her two “colleagues” Lisa and Chelsea go in search of the legendary bigfoot when a sensational news story comes to their attention. It turns out another girl and her girlfriends went missing in the woods. Only one girl made it out, badly hurt and badly “damaged.” One of the professor’s colleagues comes back with the girl’s tablet, containing a very interesting picture of a very interesting creature…
name: The Woods Have Eyes
Hoch den Rüssel - hau rein in die Schüssel!

description:
April 4, 2029: the judicial system, overwhelmed by the upsurge in petty crimes, provides cryonics of trial detainees. Former oil platforms are then converted into off-shore prisons.

March 12, 2053: Naoko Sonoda made the headlines. She is the first cryo-escaped in history.
name: Jukurpa

description: The Crimson Code is, in 2056, at the highest alert level during a threat of nuclear attack. The alert is maximum after the attack in London that leads to the downfall of the European economy and a major energy crisis.
name: Crimson Code

description: The GMB (Genetically Modified Beings) lead a political struggle demanding their existence to be respected. A consequence of the inclusion of their claims will screen Carmen to a suicide mission.
name: L'Appel de Baïkonour

volume.name: Als die Zombies die Welt auffrassen

description: He's been waiting for you!
name: Mummy in the Iron Mask!
